{"tid":1186154,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有一日老師叫小明番屋企問下屋企人1+1等於幾！","createTime":"2019-06-04T17:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T04:19:50.000Z","uid":43785,"like":44,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b79831293cee7b062d4a23e9457c0c0b8967c5b9","tid":1186154,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:36:07.000Z","msg":"從前有個人叫小明 ，<br />\n有一日老師叫小明番屋企問下屋企1+1等於幾多，<br />\n小明番到屋企之後，就見到牙媽係廚房，佢就問牙媽:1+1等於幾多？ 牙媽煮緊飯：加d糖加d鹽加d胡椒粉落去<br />\n<br />\n然後小明見到老豆又問佢：1+1等於幾多？ 老豆睇緊馬：快d快d<br />\n<br />\n然後小明見到家姐又問佢：1+1等於幾多？ 家姐好專心沖緊涼係唱歌：我捨不得你～yeah~yeah~<br />\n<br />\n第二日<br />\n小明番到學校老師就問佢<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;🏫：小明1+1等於幾多？ <br />\n👦🏻：加d糖加d鹽加d胡椒粉落去<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;🏫 : 你信吾信我趕你出校丫？<br />\n👦🏻 : 快d快d<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;🏫 : 我依家踢你出校<br />\n👦🏻 : 我捨不得你～yeah~yeah~"},{"pid":"36d4a6812b3f0c31fbfcc7780f4b156851fc95e4","tid":1186154,"uid":144,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:38:40.000Z","msg":"啪左咩黎 我又要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4189e5405178f43d0532d872b0c1c733bc85dc7a","tid":1186154,"uid":2377,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:55:41.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"fe30be91826ea4c091d7ddd801d632a44b55661b","tid":1186154,"uid":243854,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mO31ntJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmO31ntJ.jpg&h=a40b0723&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"950347b05e9da6c15d9f5d277ba00ed174c982ae","tid":1186154,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:59:06.000Z","msg":"笑到爆肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809d1b67af4aae590589f3569aea00a1d2058d9a","tid":1186154,"uid":1654,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T18:20:50.000Z","msg":"小學年代連flash game 都